data.meta_description: Lebanese beauties Dominique Youssef Hourani دومينيك حوراني   who was born August 7, 1985, is the daughter of Lebanese historian, renowned archaeologist and writer who wrote more than 20 books Dr. Youssef Hourani and the wife of Austrian naturalized Iranian businessman Ali Reza Almassi. Dominique Hourani is a Lebanese singer actress, model and designer, she was also an international beauty pageant title holder when she won the 32nd Miss Intercontinental pageant
